     <title> Pseude class selector </title>
<style>
/* Unvisited link */
      a:link{
      color:red;
      }
/* Visited link */
      a:visited{
      color:green;
      }
/* Mouse over link */
      a:hover{
      color:hotpink;
      }
/* Selected link */
      a:active{
      colro:blue;
      }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <p><b><a href="default.asp" target="_blink">This is a link </a></b></p>
    <p><b>Note:</b>a:hover must come afer a:link and a:visited in the css definition in order to be effective.
    </p>
    <p><b>Note:</b>a:active must come after a:hover  in the css definition in order to be effective.</p>
</body>
